{"tid":2078423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾到機場乘客及打工仔或已被感染？何栢良：任由密切接觸者滯留機場禁區5日是防疫漏洞","createTime":"2020-06-25T04:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T04:47:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c94450e3f02f6291eccbd5e3c1e0ea43da0881e","tid":2078423,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534049-20200625.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534049-20200625.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=b78ea92a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534049-20200625.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=99e205dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534049-20200625.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n一班日前由迪拜到港的航機，有26人先後確診新型肺炎，11名同機的內地人，打算經香港轉機返內地，但無登機證，在本港機場滯留約5天。據了解，其中10人已經被送往檢疫中心，另1人就已於昨日返回迪拜。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良說，任由這批密切接觸者滯留機場禁區，是防疫的漏洞，政府有需要檢討。"}]}